# Plans and specs location

Use these directories for all new planning and specification documents:

| Artifact | Path |
|----------|------|
| **Plans** (implementation plans, roadmaps, step-by-step work) | `docs/features/plans/` |
| **Specs** (design docs, requirements, architecture notes) | `docs/features/specs/` |

## Naming

Prefer dated, kebab-case filenames so files sort chronologically, for example:

- `docs/features/plans/2026-04-17-example-feature.md`
- `docs/features/specs/2026-04-17-example-feature-design.md`

## Do not use for new work

Do **not** create new plans or specs under `docs/superpowers/plans/` or `docs/superpowers/specs/`. That layout came from the Superpowers plugin; this project standardizes on **`docs/features/`** instead.

If you open or edit existing files still under `docs/superpowers/`, consider moving them to the matching path under `docs/features/` and updating any internal links.
